DF : 

    SEE DISK FILE SYSTEM : df

    SHOW TOTAL IN LAST LINE : df --total OR du -c

    EXCLUDE TMPFS FILE SYSTEM : df -x tmpfs

    SEE INODES WITH FILE SYSTEM : df -i


DU : 

    SEE SUBDIRECTORIES AND DIRECTORY USAGE : du /Path/To/Files/Folders

    SEE ALL DIRECTORIES AND FILES USAGE : du -a

    SUMMARIZES USAGE BY DIRECTORY : du -s

    USE NCDU : ncdu


DD : 

    COPY ONE FILE TO OTHER : dd if=/Path/inputfile of=/Path/outputfile

    COPY EACH BLOCKSIZE AT A TIME : dd if=/Path/inputfile of=/Path/outputfile bs=N




